\qj \hyphpar0 \cbpat0 {\sa60\sb60\li0\ri0\fi0\sl288\slmult1 \f10 \fs20 \cf1 \b0 \i0 \strike0 \ul0 {\f10 \fs20 \cf1 \b0 \i0 \strike0 \ul0 117.} On the first day of trial, Mr\u8205\? Lee informed the court that P was abandoning his claim for post-trial loss of earnings and that he was no longer pursing item\u8205\? (3) in the sum of $2,028,511.80 thereby reducing his claim by the said sum.\par}

\qj \hyphpar0 \cbpat0 {\sa60\sb60\li0\ri0\fi0\sl288\slmult1 \f10 \fs20 \cf1 \b0 \i0 \strike0 \ul0 {\f10 \fs20 \cf1 \b0 \i0 \strike0 \ul0 118.} P was admitted to hospital on 17\u8205\? July 2013 and was discharged two days later on 19\u8205\? July 2013. There is no dispute about the injuries he sustained and these are well documented in the medical reports in evidence.\par}

