\qj \hyphpar0 \cbpat0 {\sa60\sb60\li0\ri0\fi0\sl288\slmult1 \f10 \fs20 \cf1 \b0 \i0 \strike0 \ul0 {\f10 \fs20 \cf1 \b0 \i0 \strike0 \ul0 123.} X-ray of the chest showed that the fractures had healed with satisfactory alignment. There was no lung lesion detected.\par}

\qj \hyphpar0 \cbpat0 {\sa60\sb60\li0\ri0\fi0\sl288\slmult1 \f10 \fs20 \cf1 \b0 \i0 \strike0 \ul0 {\f10 \fs20 \cf1 \b0 \i0 \strike0 \ul0 124.} They were satisfied that P had sustained an injury to his chest on 17\u8205\? July 2013. Their diagnosis was non-displaced fracture over right 5th to 7th\u8205\? ribs and left 3rd\u8205\? rib.\par}

